 other allied activities; and import and trading of aluminum scrap. The company was formerly known as Umred Agro Complex Limited and changed its name to CIAN Agro Industries & Infrastructure Limited in December 2015. CIAN Agro Industries & Infrastructure Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Nagpur, India."}}